properties.text: Covid 19 is spreading all over the globe. Everyone should follow the CDC guidelines in order to avoid getting infected. However, there are always some people who don't believe in how serious the problem is. They are not wearing a mask, not using sanitizer, and may ultimately get infected. If you meet someone like this, please help them and the environment...

DON'T WASTE BULLETS. NEVER LEAVE THE LAST BULLET TO YOUR ENEMY.                                       You have to kill all infected people to win the game. If you jump into a trap or run into an infected person, you will lose a life and be sent to the most recent checkpoint. If you run out of bullets, the game is over.
Hold the up arrow for an extended jump and press it twice to double jump.
